Subject: [PATCH 27/35] irqchip/gic-v4.1: Plumb set_vcpu_affinity SGI callbacks
Date:   Mon, 23 Sep 2019 19:25:58 +0100
Message-Id: <20190923182606.32100-28-maz@kernel.org>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.20.1
